Sentencas: Dense yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte films were successfully fabricated onto anode substrates using a modified dry pressing process.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cells with dense yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte membranes fabricated by a dry pressing process

Sentencas: The film thickness was uniform, and could be readily controlled by the mass of the nanocrystalline YSZ powders.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cells with dense yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte membranes fabricated by a dry pressing process

Sentencas: The electrolyte films adhered well to the anode substrates by controlling the anode composition.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cells with dense yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte membranes fabricated by a dry pressing process

Sentencas: An anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) with a dense YSZ electrolyte film of 8 mu m in thickness was operated at temperatures from 700 to 800 degrees C using humidified (3 vol% H2O) hydrogen as fuel and air as oxidant.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cells with dense yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte membranes fabricated by a dry pressing process

Sentencas: An open circuit voltage of 1.06 V and a maximum power density of 791 mW cm(-2) were achieved at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cells with dense yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte membranes fabricated by a dry pressing process

Sentencas: The results indicate that the gas permeation through the electrolyte film was negligible, and that good performance can be obtained by this simple and cost-effective technique which can significantly reduce the fabrication cost of SOFCs.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cells with dense yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte membranes fabricated by a dry pressing process
